text: Impressive field and gym! The gym was well furnished and I saw a huge variety of machines. They have a swimming pool too, which I didn’t see but I’m sure is great

I love the open running area . It has a fitness corner that you can use too. If you need to shower, there are shower facilities around. There's a water cooler and vending machine right near the sports hall too. Really great place to have a quick jog!
School must have sport stadium.. make it perfect for students to do their exercises.

Very nice track to train at, not very crowded even during peak timings.

Open to public and accessible by public transport. Short 10 minutes walk from Expo MRT.
Huge stadium and jogging track for training
